A python API to MtGox

=Python API Tutorial=

=Command line tools=

Last price on MtGox:
#pygox_spot

Sell a bitcoin for $10
#pygox_sell 1@10 

Sell one bitcoin in a series of sell orders from 10.00 to 10.99 
#pygox_sell 0.01@10.00 0.01@10.01 ... 

Bash users can write:
#pygox_sell 0.01@10.{0..9}{0..9}

(Really, try echo 0.01@10.{0..9}{0..9}) to see what this bit of bash magic does.


